DON'T EAT THIS. UH-UH.
NOW WE HAVE SOME DELICIOUS
HOMEMADE FOOD OVER THERE.

283
00:18:04,295 --> 00:18:06,562
COME ON OVER.
IT'S SO GOOD.
YEAH, COME ON.

284
00:18:06,630 --> 00:18:10,300
COME ON, WILLARD.
OH, CHICKEN. MM!
HI.

285
00:18:10,367 --> 00:18:14,520
<i>COME ON. COME ON.
GOOD BOY. COME ON.
BRING YOUR FRIEND.</i>

286
00:18:14,588 --> 00:18:17,389
YOU WON'T GET
ANY OF THAT HERE.
WHAT'S THAT?

287
00:18:17,458 --> 00:18:19,692
DANCIN'.
THERE'S NO DANCIN'. RIGHT?
THAT'S RIGHT.

288
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:22,695
WHY?
IT'S ILLEGAL.

289
