ABOUT FIVE OR SIX YEARS.
WHY?</i>

291
00:18:28,769 --> 00:18:30,970
GO AHEAD. TELL HIM.

292
00:18:31,038 --> 00:18:33,940
STARTED WHEN A BUNCH OF KIDS
GOT KILLED IN A CAR WRECK.

293
00:18:34,008 --> 00:18:38,744
<i>WHOLE TOWN WENT BANANAS,
BLAMING IT ON THE MUSIC
AND THE LIQUOR AND DANCING.</i>

294
00:18:38,812 --> 00:18:41,948
NOW THEY'RE JUST CONVINCED
IT'S ALL A SIN.

295
00:18:42,016 --> 00:18:46,085
WHO'S CONVINCED?
WHOLE DAMN TOWN.

296
00:18:52,109 --> 00:18:54,410
SO, YOU REALLY CAN'T
DANCE HERE, MAN.

297
00:18:54,478 --> 00:18:57,213
I CAN'T BELIEVE THAT.
IT'S TRUE.

298
00:18:57,281 --> 00:18:59,549
