- COULD YOU TELL ME
WHAT THE PROBLEM IS?

318
00:19:59,193 --> 00:20:02,562
<i>WILL YOU JUST STEP OUT
OF THE CAR, PLEASE?</i>

319
00:20:02,629 --> 00:20:05,982
HEY, JIM, THESE PLATES
ARE ILLINOIS STATE.
SO?

320
00:20:06,049 --> 00:20:07,800
