00:20:14,508 --> 00:20:16,442
IS THERE A LAW
AGAINST LOUD MUSIC?

324
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:18,677
HEY, LET'S WATCH
THAT ATTITUDE, BOY.

325
00:20:18,745 --> 00:20:20,813
THIS WAY, I DON'T
HAVE TO TAKE YOU IN.

326
00:20:20,881 --> 00:20:23,616
TWENTY-FIVE DOLLARS.
THEY WOULDN'T EVEN
LET ME OFF WITH A WARNING.

327
00:20:23,683 --> 00:20:26,619
YOU CAN'T TALK TO OUR POLICE
THE WAY YOU TALK TO
THOSE BIG CITY POLICE.

328
00:20:26,686 --> 00:20:29,021
- BUT I WASN'T DOING ANYTHING.
- YEAH, SURE.

329
00:20:29,089 --> 00:20:33,008
SARAH, HUSH. REN, THERE WAS
THIS BUNCH OF KIDS SNUCK OVER
THE STATE LINE...

330
00:20:33,076 --> 00:20:35,578
A YEAR OR SO AGO
TO SEE SOME ROCK-AND-ROLL GROUP,

331
00:20:35,646 --> 00:20:39,615
