WHAT CAME OVER ME.

343
00:21:34,404 --> 00:21:38,024
YOU KNOW, I CAN'T ALWAYS
BE WITH YOU, ARIEL.

344
00:21:38,092 --> 00:21:40,877
I CAN'T ALWAYS
LOOK OUT FOR YOU.

345
00:21:49,686 --> 00:21:53,256
