USED THE WORD PANSY.

369
00:23:25,432 --> 00:23:28,050
WHOO! HE GOT YOU
ON THAT ONE, CHUCK.
SHUT UP!

370
00:23:28,117 --> 00:23:31,404
[Chuck]
