TO PISS ME OFF?

378
00:23:58,014 --> 00:24:01,217
WELL, BOY, A LOT OF FOLKS
ARE GONNA GIVE YOU PROBLEMS
RIGHT OFF,

379
00:24:01,284 --> 00:24:03,519
BECAUSE, YOU SEE,
YOU'RE AN OUTSIDER.

380
00:24:03,587 --> 00:24:06,655
YOU'RE DANGEROUS.
THEY'RE ALWAYS GONNA
WORRY ABOUT YOU.

381
00:24:06,723 --> 00:24:11,477
SCREW 'EM. AND THIS IS ONLY
ONE LITTLE CORNER OF THE WORLD.

382
00:24:14,530 --> 00:24:16,215
START THURSDAY?

383
00:24:17,785 --> 00:24:20,886
- SOUNDS OKAY.
- YES!

384
00:24:22,856 --> 00:24:24,790
