385
00:24:27,844 --> 00:24:30,846
HARD WORK,
BUT YOU'LL GET USED TO IT.

386
00:24:33,083 --> 00:24:35,017
[Grunts]

387
00:24:42,575 --> 00:24:45,561
<i>OH, HI, ARIEL.</i>

388
00:24:45,629 --> 00:24:47,563
<i>CHUCK CRANSTON
WANTS TO SEE YOU.</i>

389
00:24:47,630 --> 00:24:50,866
MEET HIM OVER AT THE BACK
OF HIS DADDY'S FIELD TOMORROW.

390
00:24:50,934 --> 00:24:54,920
<i>5:30.
SO, WHAT HAPPENS TOMORROW
AT 5:30?</i>

391
00:24:56,456 --> 00:24:59,258
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
SHOW UP TO FIND OUT.

392
00:24:59,325 --> 00:25:02,662
- IF I DON'T?
