398
00:25:20,180 --> 00:25:21,931
HEY, MacCORMACK,
WHERE THE HELL ARE YOU?

399
00:25:23,733 --> 00:25:25,867
YOU KNOW HER?

400
00:25:25,935 --> 00:25:31,423
[Grunts]
AND SO SHE TELLS ME THAT--

401
00:25:31,491 --> 00:25:33,625
THAT I PISSED
CHUCK OFF, RIGHT?

402
00:25:33,693 --> 00:25:36,828
SO, HE WANTS TO SEE ME,
AND SHE WALKS AWAY.

403
00:25:36,897 --> 00:25:40,266
HE FIGURED YOU WERE GONNA
CHICKEN AND NEVER--
OOH, IMPRESSIVE!

404
00:25:40,334 --> 00:25:44,153
NO. KIND OF OUT OF IT.

405
00:25:45,856 --> 00:25:48,290
I HAD TO GO
TO WORK LAST YEAR.

406
00:25:48,358 --> 00:25:50,292
WELL, YOU'RE STILL MOVIN'.

407
00:25:50,360 --> 00:25:53,729
OOH, YOU'D BETTER WATCH THAT.
ARIEL'S GONNA TELL HER POP,
AND YOU'RE GONNA BURN.

408
00:25:55,498 --> 00:25:59,518
YEAH, WHAT'S HER STORY?
IS SHE REALLY TOUGH, OR WHAT?

