♪ I'M FREE
♪ HEAVEN HELPS THE MAN

1358
01:32:04,543 --> 01:32:06,710
♪ WHO FIGHTS HIS FEAR

1359
01:32:09,514 --> 01:32:11,449
YOU LOOK VERY NICE.
OH, NO.

1360
01:32:11,516 --> 01:32:13,484
YES, YOU DO.
NO.
[Chuckling]

1361
01:32:13,552 --> 01:32:15,486
YES, YOU LOOK
VERY NICE.
NO.

1362
01:32:15,554 --> 01:32:17,721
YES, YOU DO.
YOU LOOK WONDERFUL.
NO-- YOU THINK?

1363
01:32:17,789 --> 01:32:20,424
- YEAH. MM-HMM.
- [Sighs]

1364
01:32:21,860 --> 01:32:24,862
NO.
[Sighs]

1365
01:32:24,929 --> 01:32:28,949
YOU CAN'T VERY WELL
GO TO A PROM WITHOUT A CORSAGE.

1366
01:32:29,017 --> 01:32:31,552
[Both Laughing]

1367
01:32:32,754 --> 01:32:34,688
THIS IS GORGEOUS!

1368
01:32:35,757 --> 01:32:39,827
MOM!
[Sniffs]

1369
01:32:39,895 --> 01:32:42,696
WHERE DO YOU THINK
I SHOULD--
HERE'S A WRIST THING HERE.

1370
01:32:42,764 --> 01:32:45,198
OH, MOM,
YOU REALLY DIDN'T HAVE TO.

1371
01:32:45,266 --> 01:32:47,200
I DIDN'T.

1372
01:32:50,038 --> 01:32:53,140
NOW DON'T GO ON TO HIM ABOUT IT
'CAUSE HE'LL ONLY DENY IT.

1373
01:33:05,921 --> 01:33:10,158
HEY, I WAS GONNA
COME UP AND GET-- I WAS...

1374
01:33:11,043 --> 01:33:13,544
<i>GONNA COME UP AND GET YOU.</i>

1375
01:33:13,611 --> 01:33:15,563
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

1376
01:33:16,965 --> 01:33:18,900
YOU'RE BEAUTIFUL.

1377
01:33:21,437 --> 01:33:23,805
WHAT?

1378
01:33:31,012 --> 01:33:35,749
I-- I MEAN IT.
YOU ARE BEAUTIFUL.

1379
01:33:42,023 --> 01:33:44,292
COME ON.

1380
01:33:47,395 --> 01:33:49,330
[Chuckles]

1381
01:33:54,169 --> 01:33:56,403
THANK YOU.

1382
01:33:56,471 --> 01:33:58,405
[Clears Throat]

1383
01:34:03,211 --> 01:34:05,379
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA,
WHOA, WHOA!

1384
01:34:42,450 --> 01:34:46,854
♪ I THOUGHT THAT DREAMS BELONGED
TO OTHER MEN ♪

1385
01:34:48,823 --> 01:34:52,526
♪ 'CAUSE EACH TIME I GOT CLOSE

1386
01:34:52,594 --> 01:34:55,996
♪ THEY'D FALL APART AGAIN

1387
01:34:57,331 --> 01:35:01,602
♪ I FEARED MY HEART
WOULD BEAT IN SECRECY ♪

1388
01:35:03,738 --> 01:35:07,391
♪ I FACED THE NIGHTS ALONE

1389
01:35:07,459 --> 01:35:11,061
♪ OH, HOW COULD I HAVE KNOWN

1390
01:35:11,129 --> 01:35:16,633
♪ THAT ALL MY LIFE
I ONLY NEEDED YOU ♪

1391
01:35:16,701 --> 01:35:21,472
♪ OH, ALMOST PARADISE

1392
01:35:21,540 --> 01:35:24,174
♪ WE'RE KNOCKIN'
ON HEAVEN'S DOOR ♪

1393
01:35:25,343 --> 01:35:28,028
♪ ALMOST PARADISE

1394
01:35:29,430 --> 01:35:33,266
♪ HOW COULD WE ASK FOR MORE

1395
01:35:33,334 --> 01:35:37,471
♪ I SWEAR
THAT I CAN SEE FOREVER ♪

1396
01:35:37,538 --> 01:35:41,091
♪ IN YOUR EYES

1397
01:35:41,159 --> 01:35:44,962
♪ PARADISE

1398
01:35:49,368 --> 01:35:54,104
♪ IT SEEMS LIKE PERFECT LOVE'S
SO HARD TO FIND ♪

1399
01:35:56,307 --> 01:35:58,059
♪ [Continues, Indistinct]

1400
01:36:05,133 --> 01:36:07,401
WELL, LET'S
TAKE A CLOSER LOOK.

1401
01:36:07,469 --> 01:36:09,737
NO, SHE'LL THINK
I'M CHECKING UP AGAIN.

1402
01:36:09,805 --> 01:36:12,473
NO. SHE WON'T EVEN KNOW
WE'RE HERE. COME ON.

1403
01:36:17,312 --> 01:36:20,431
YOU'RE THE LAST FOLKS I EXPECTED
TO SEE AROUND HERE TONIGHT.

1404
01:36:20,499 --> 01:36:23,133
EVENING, ANDY.
HI, ANDY.

1405
01:36:23,201 --> 01:36:25,369
HI. REVEREND,
YOU DONE A GOOD THING HERE.

1406
01:36:25,437 --> 01:36:28,505
WELL, I'M STILL NOT SURE
IT WAS THE RIGHT THING.

1407
01:36:28,573 --> 01:36:30,257
COMES CLOSE.

1408
01:36:47,275 --> 01:36:49,209
SHAW.

1409
01:36:52,013 --> 01:36:53,947
SHAW?

1410
01:36:57,719 --> 01:37:01,288
SHAW, WHAT IS IT?

1411
01:37:05,994 --> 01:37:10,564
IT'S JUST
THE TWO OF US AGAIN, HUH?

1412
01:37:26,898 --> 01:37:30,700
SHAW.
WHAT?

1413
01:37:30,768 --> 01:37:34,871
<i>WE'RE ALMOST DANCING.
♪ ALMOST PARADISE </i>

1414
01:37:34,940 --> 01:37:36,873
[Chuckles]

1415
01:37:42,480 --> 01:37:45,249
HI, RUSTY.
HI!

1416
01:37:55,460 --> 01:37:58,212
HELLO, WILLARD.

1417
01:37:58,280 --> 01:38:00,414
YOU PROMISED
YOU WOULDN'T FIGHT.

1418
01:38:00,482 --> 01:38:03,183
DON'T YOU LOOK SWEET.
[Laughs]

1419
01:38:04,753 --> 01:38:06,887
WHAT DO YOU WANT, CHUCK?

1420
01:38:06,955 --> 01:38:09,656
OH, I GOT A LITTLE BUSINESS
WITH YOUR FRIEND MacCORMACK.

1421
01:38:09,724 --> 01:38:12,392
HEY, CHUCK, COOL IT, ALL RIGHT?
NO FIGHTS TONIGHT, OKAY?

1422
01:38:13,428 --> 01:38:16,597
HEY, NO FIGHTS, FELLAS.
[Laughter]

1423
01:38:16,664 --> 01:38:19,916
[Chuck]
SURE, WILLARD.

1424
01:38:19,984 --> 01:38:22,052
ALL RIGHT.

1425
01:38:24,322 --> 01:38:28,626
- CUTE. NO FIGHTS, WILLARD.
- AH! DAMN, MAN!

1426
01:38:28,694 --> 01:38:33,263
<i>I TOLD YOU, ALL RIGHT.
I PROMISED RUSTY NO FIGHTS
TONIGHT, OKAY?</i>

1427
01:38:33,331 --> 01:38:36,850
- [Screaming, Indistinct]
- [Chuck Grunting]

1428
01:38:36,918 --> 01:38:39,603
<i>[Rusty] OH, WILLARD!
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO,
RUSTY?</i>

1429
01:38:39,671 --> 01:38:43,056
KILL THE SON OF A BITCH!
HELP, SOMEBODY!

1430
01:38:43,124 --> 01:38:46,276
[Grunting Continues]

1431
01:38:46,344 --> 01:38:50,748
- CHUCK!
- HEY, IT'S MR. DANCE FEVER!

1432
01:38:50,816 --> 01:38:53,334
YEAH, YOU'RE A GODDAMN HERO
WHEN IT'S FIVE TO ONE!

1433
01:38:53,401 --> 01:38:56,220
[Grunting, Shouting]

1434
01:38:56,287 --> 01:38:58,756
BEAT THE SHIT OUT OF HIM!

1435
01:38:58,823 --> 01:39:01,342
[Indistinct Shouting]

1436
01:39:05,697 --> 01:39:09,683
- [Yells]
- [Grunts]

1437
01:39:09,751 --> 01:39:11,251
BASTARD!

1438
01:39:15,506 --> 01:39:18,525
WE'RE GONNA DANCE NOW,
MacCORMACK, HUH?

1439
01:39:18,592 --> 01:39:22,762
[Grunting Continues]

1440
01:39:28,736 --> 01:39:31,988
[Rusty]
YEAH! WHOA!
[Ariel] ALL RIGHT!

1441
01:39:36,294 --> 01:39:38,228
HEY, HANDSOME.
GREAT DANCE, MAN.

1442
01:39:38,296 --> 01:39:40,230
[Laughing]
OUR HEROES!

1443
